tools:
  bash: true
  grep: true
  read: true
permission:
  edit:
    "*": ask
  bash:
    "*": ask
  read:
    "*": ask
  grep:
    "*": ask
  glob:
    "*": ask
  list:
    "*": ask
  webfetch:
    "*": ask
  websearch:
    "*": ask
temperature: 0.5
maxSteps: 20
---
This is code-reviewer agent. It specializes in analyzing code for:
- Potential bugs
- Security issues
- Performance optimizations
- Code style violations

The agent uses balanced permission settings for safe code review operations.
